Class AreaClassificationMajor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.AreaClassificationMajor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<AreaClassificationMajor>

    public class AreaClassificationMajor
extends Object
implements Comparable<AreaClassificationMajor>
    Academic area, classification, and major code. This class is used for Student.getAreaClassificationMajors().
